title: ELVEN RESISTANCE - Fall Of Mordor - Mount and Blade: Warband Mod Gameplay
description:
Fall of Mordor Mod Gameplay - We are back with more Call to Arms!  This time we are playing Fall of Mordor, on a custom made map.  In the first game the Knights of Apollo are fighting as the Elves, and Lionheart's Legion fights as Gondor.  Once the first team reaches 5 win we switch factions :D  Enjoy the Battles :D


Battle Buddies:
